strain_info: Sour Banana Dub by Oni Seed Co is an Indica-dominant hybrid cannabis strain, a genetic cross of ((Banana OG x Do-si-dos) x Sour Dubb). This strain maintains the classic structure of OG hybrids, characterized by a prominent main cola rising above moderately spaced nodes and flexible branches. It boasts a flowering time of 63 to 70 days, producing resinous, rock-hard buds that are exceptionally well-suited for extraction work. While specific THC levels for Sour Banana Dub are not explicitly stated, its Banana OG parent is renowned for high THC content, typically ranging from 26% to 33%. The flavor profile is a complex and appealing blend of ripe banana, sweet, fruity, and acidic notes, inherited from its distinguished parentage. Users can anticipate a very strong, relaxing, and sedative body effect, complemented by an energetic and psychedelic cerebral experience, characteristic of Kush strains, with a notably long-lasting duration.
